{"word":"Dress","slug":"dress","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dress</b> Of fig leaves<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=7'>Gen 3:7</a><br/> Of skins<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=21'>Gen 3:21</a><br/><a href='S:Hair'>Hair</a>; <a href='S:Goat, Hair of'>Goat, Hair of</a>; <a href='S:Leather'>Leather</a>; <a href='S:Linen'>Linen</a>; <a href='S:Sackcloth'>Sackcloth</a>; <a href='S:Silk'>Silk</a>; <a href='S:Wool'>Wool</a><br/> Mixed materials in, forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=11'>Deu 22:11</a><br/> Men forbidden to wear women's, and women forbidden to wear men's<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=5'>Deu 22:5</a><br/> Rules with respect to women's<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=10'>1Ti 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=3&verse=3'>1Pe 3:3</a><br/> Not to be held over night as a pledge for debt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=26'>Exo 22:26</a><br/> Ceremonial purification of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=32'>Lev 11:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=59'>Lev 13:59</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=20'>Num 31:20</a><br/><a href='S:Mourning'>Mourning</a><br/> Of the head:<br/> - Bonnets:<br/> b Prescribed by Moses, for the priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=40'>Exo 28:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=9'>Exo 29:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=28'>Exo 39:28</a><br/> b Prescribed by Ezekiel, for the priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=18'>Eze 44:18</a><br/> b Worn by women<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=20'>Isa 3:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=24&verse=17'>Eze 24:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=24&verse=23'>Eze 24:23</a><br/> - Hats worn by men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=21'>Dan 3:21</a> <br/> - Hoods<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=23'>Isa 3:23</a> <br/> - Kerchiefs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=13&verse=18'>Eze 13:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=13&verse=21'>Eze 13:21</a> <br/> Various articles of:<br/> - Mantle:<br/> b General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=3'>Ezr 9:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=13'>1Ki 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=27'>1Ch 15:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=1&verse=20'>Job 1:20</a><br/> b Many colored<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=18'>2Sa 13:18</a><br/> b Purple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=2'>Joh 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=5'>Joh 19:5</a><br/> - Robe<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=4'>Exo 28:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=4'>1Sa 18:4</a> <br/> - Shawls<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=22'>Isa 3:22</a> <br/> - Embroidered coat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=4'>Exo 28:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=40'>Exo 28:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=19'>1Sa 2:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=21'>Dan 3:21</a> <br/> - Sleeveless shirt, called coat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=5&verse=40'>Mat 5:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=29'>Luk 6:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=23'>Joh 19:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=39'>Act 9:39</a> <br/> - Cloak<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=13'>2Ti 4:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=2'>Joh 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=5'>Joh 19:5</a> <br/> - Hosen<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=21'>Dan 3:21</a> <br/> - Skirts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=5&verse=3'>Eze 5:3</a> <br/> - Mufflers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=19'>Isa 3:19</a> <br/> - Wimples (satchels)<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=22'>Isa 3:22</a> <br/> - Sashes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=20'>Isa 3:20</a><br/><a href='S:Veil'>Veil</a> <br/> Changes of raiment, the folly of excessive<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=27&verse=16'>Job 27:16</a><br/> Uniform vestments kept in store:<br/> - For worshipers of Baal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=23'>2Ki 10:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=1&verse=8'>Zep 1:8</a> <br/> - For wedding feasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=11'>Mat 22:11</a> <br/> Presents made of changes of raiment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=45&verse=22'>Gen 45:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=4'>1Sa 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=5'>2Ki 5:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=6&verse=8'>Est 6:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=7'>Dan 5:7</a><br/><a href='S:Priest'>Priest</a><br/> Vestments of mourning<br/> <a href='S:Mourning'>Mourning</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Filthy, of unrighteousness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=64&verse=6'>Isa 64:6</a> <br/> - Of righteousness and of iniquity<br/> <a href='S:Colors'>Colors</a> <br/> Symbolic, filthy, of iniquity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=3&verse=4'>Zec 3:4</a>"}]}